25 // NOTE that the 0xFFFF of 0xFF entries at the end of some tables below are
26 // not properly list terminators, but are actually the printable definitions
27 // of values that are legitimately found on the PCI bus. The size
28 // definitions should be used for loop control when the table is searched.
29
